prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook Ecosystem Overview
prompt.content: The Promptbook ecosystem includes a runtime engine (available as npm packages and a Docker image), a web-based editor (Promptbook.studio, currently in MVP), and community support channels (Discord, GitHub, LinkedIn, Facebook, and branded social media).
